      Get news delivered, automagically.
      <!-- Free template for <span class="hidden xl:inline">creating websites with</span>
      <span class="text-accent dark:text-white highlight"> Astro 2.0</span> + Tailwind CSS -->
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      <span class="hidden sm:inline">
        <span class="font-semibold">MonitoRSS</span> is a free and open-source bot that delivers customized news straight to your Discord server.</span
