          'Get notified of updates, releases, or discounts from your favorite game developers and publishers.',
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:steam',
      },
      {
        title: 'Weather',
        description:
          'Plan ahead by getting weather forecasts or alerts to stay safe.',
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:landscape',
      },
      {
        title: 'Anime',
        description:
          'Get notified when a new episode of your favorite anime is released.',
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:reading-ebook',
      },
    ]}
